(34, 1, '34.jpg', 'Mourinho\'s men makes a huge statement aheead of Fa cup clash with a winðŸ™ŒðŸ™Œ', '\n<p>\n   A good day for Manchester united as they gave a well deserved victory to their fans to cheer up. \r\n</p>\n\n<p>\n   \r\n</p>\n\n<p>\n   Having giving Manchester city the league trophy on Sunday afternoon with a poor performance at home to west brom, mourinho\'s men went to the vitality stadium and took all three points.\r\n</p>\n\n<p>\n   \r\n</p>\n\n<p>\n   Goals from smalling in the 28th minute and Lukaku in the 70th minutes made sure three points were secured. A nice cross at the edge of the penalty area from lingard was enough for Smalling to slide in the ball at the back of the net. Lukaku coming from the bench in the 63rd minute to net the winner.\r\n</p>\n\n<p>\n   \r\n</p>\n\n<p>\n   Their win on Wednesday night takes them to four points clear above Liverpool in third place with four games remaining.\r\n</p>\n\n<p>\n   \r\n</p>\n\n<p>\n   This win will give a huge boost going into their Fa Cup semi final clash against Tottenham on Saturday.\n</p>\n', 4, '2018-04-18 17:17:46', 'APPROVED'),
(35, 1, '35.jpg', 'Late Ronaldo\'s flick denies Athletic a victory at the bernabau stadium', '\n<p>\n   Ronaldo\'s late goal denies Athletico Bilbao from getting a victory at the bernabau stadium. The match which Real Madrid needed a win left it late to secure a draw.\r\n</p>\n\n<p>\n   \r\n</p>\n\n<p>\n   The Athletic side started the match on a bright note with Williams netting a super goal in the 13th minutes. Real Madrid would have conceded more thanks to the wood work for keeping out a shot from entering the back of the net.\r\n</p>\n\n<p>\n   \r\n</p>\n\n<p>\n   Real Madrid kept pushing for the equalizer throwing all men forward to get a goal. It paid off when Luka modric fired a low shot with Ronaldo using his right leg to tap it at the back of the net. Real Madrid will now head into the semifinal big clash against Bayern Munich in the champions league.\n</p>\n', 4, '2018-04-18 17:56:20', 'APPROVED'),
